  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/a2c83c00f5477d1cc2a6fdacbada51f2.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 /></span><br><br>[13 Seconds] is a hardcore bullet hell Roguelike game.<br><br><br>You have participated in a robot game known for its ruthlessness and harshness. You must survive while dodging bullets from countless destruction machines until the end of 13 levels.<br>Participants who ultimately succeed in surviving will receive corresponding rewards. It's definitely worth a try!<br><br>There's just one minor problem: the only robot you have is a package delivery drone...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You must use both hands to operate both robots at the same time.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As the game progresses, more and more attack machines will appear, pushing you to your limits. If either robot is destroyed, you lose.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various items are randomly dropped during the game. If used well, it will help you survive.<br><br><br>Will you be able to reach the ultimate level 13?<br>... And is level 13 really the end?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/a2c83c00f5477d1cc2a6fdacbada51f2.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 /></span><br><br>[13 Seconds] is a hardcore bullet hell Roguelike game.<br><br><br>You have participated in a robot game known for its ruthlessness and harshness. You must survive while dodging bullets from countless destruction machines until the end of 13 levels.<br>Participants who ultimately succeed in surviving will receive corresponding rewards. It's definitely worth a try!<br><br>There's just one minor problem: the only robot you have is a package delivery drone...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4d6d039c250b248519720f315d2ecb4f.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You must use both hands to operate both robots at the same time.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/4611bd7a0f7edc4fbc2dcd873f5b7094.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As the game progresses, more and more attack machines will appear, pushing you to your limits. If either robot is destroyed, you lose.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.poster.avif?t=1710307725\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.webm?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761620/extras/0f349d038b75d2686f26644ca00506b3.mp4?t=1710307725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various items are randomly dropped during the game. If used well, it will help you survive.<br><br><br>Will you be able to reach the ultimate level 13?<br>... And is level 13 really the end?",
